{
  "texts": [
    "Many more people have written similar types of documents, such as cover letters for job applications.",
    "We connect LLM behavior to human behavior 1 to posit how extremely popular models might communicate to people \"right\" and \"wrong\" ways to describe themselves when comparing authorship demographics with AI writing style tendencies.",
    "We analyze data from two higher education contexts.",
    "The first is the University of California (UC) system, one of the largest public research university systems in the world.",
    "The application process is streamlined: students who want to apply to any of the 9 campuses that provide undergraduate degree programs only need to complete one actual application."
  ]
}